==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Greengage
<hw>Green"gage`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A kind of plum of medium size, roundish shape, greenish flesh, and
delicious flavor. It is called in France <altname>Reine
Claude</altname>, after the queen of Francis I. See
<er>Gage</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Greengill</ent>⟦br⟧
